      <title>摩根大通加入法国支付领域，与Visa竞争对手合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/jpmorgan-joins-french-payments-fray-in-tie-up-with-visa-rival</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通Co.将加入法国Cartes Bancaires CB，使该支付网络在与美国竞争对手Visa Inc.和Mastercard Inc.的竞争中更具实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/jpmorgan-joins-french-payments-fray-in-tie-up-with-visa-rival</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
